g guide.<br>Note:<br>Please pay attention to safety when you disembark from the sea on a yacht. Do not queue up and slide carefully. The captain and lifeguard should not make dangerous actions before making arrangements. As the yacht is fast and the sea is more bumpy, the elderly, weak, women, children and patients please participate carefully! )<br>80 USD/person (over 10 people)<br></td></tr><tr><td>Sinbad Submarine</td><td>115 USD/person (from 2 people)</td><td>Go to the pier and take a speedboat to the submarine platform. Take a submarine to dive into the 7-meter deep Red Sea and enjoy the mysterious and beautiful underwater world of the Red Sea. And some divers will give you a performance of feeding fish under the sea. Including pick-up and drop-off, accompanied by a Chinese guide<br>Note:<br>This program is an irritating. Due to certain pressure under the sea, for the elderly, weak, women, children and patients please participate carefully!<br>115 USD/person (from 2 people)</td></tr><tr><td>Red Sea Glass Boat Tour</td><td>70 USD/person (from 4 people)</td><td>Take a specially customized cruise ship with large sightseeing windows at the bottom of the cruise ship, which is convenient for enjoying the wonderful underwater world. Includes pick-up and drop-off, accompanied by a Chinese-speaking guide<br>Note:<br>Please pay attention to safety when boarding and disembarking the boat. Do not line up in crowds and slide carefully.<br>70 USD/person (from 4 people)</td></tr><tr><td>Luxor Hot Air Balloon</td><td>165 USD/person (2-3 people)</td><td>Depart from the hotel to the pier at around 5:00 in the morning and take a boat to the west bank of the Nile. Hot coffee, tea, and small snacks are prepared on the boat. Ride a hot air balloon to welcome the sunrise and overlook Luxor. Pass through the Habu City, Queen's Temple, Valley of the Kings and other scenic spots, and experience a different Luxor from a high altitude. After landing, a small celebration ceremony will be h