-speaking guide<br>Note:<br>Please pay attention to safety when boarding and disembarking the boat. Do not line up in crowds and slide carefully.<br>70 USD/person (from 4 people)</td></tr><tr><td>Luxor Hot Air Balloon</td><td>165 USD/person (2-3 people)</td><td>Depart from the hotel to the pier at around 5:00 in the morning and take a boat to the west bank of the Nile. Hot coffee, tea, and small snacks are prepared on the boat. Ride a hot air balloon to welcome the sunrise and overlook Luxor. Pass through the Habu City, Queen's Temple, Valley of the Kings and other scenic spots, and experience a different Luxor from a high altitude. After landing, a small celebration ceremony will be held and a certificate will be issued to the guests. Then return to the hotel by private car.<br>Special Note:<br>1. The hot air balloon is a high-risk program, please choose carefully according to your own circumstances.<br>2. The itinerary is for reference only and depends on the specific weather conditions of the day. If the hot air balloon cannot be taken due to weather conditions, the original price will be refunded!<br>3. Children under 7 years old cannot participate in this program<br>4. During the hot air balloon, the team leader and tour guide will not be accompanied at all times. Please wait patiently in order when getting on and off the hot air balloon. Do not rush to get on and off the hot air balloon and make dangerous moves to avoid accidents. Fly and cherish! 165 USD/person (2-3 people)<br><br>150 USD/person (4 people and above)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\">The programs listed above are all suggested programs. The guests choose to participate in the principle of voluntary and self-finance. Some programs may not be able to take part when the number of participants or resources is insufficient.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></dd></dl></div>", "<div class=\"bd\"><dl class=\"mod_info_box\"><dt>Expenses include</dt><dd><div class=\"tour_description_table_box\"><table class=