n (4-7 people)</td><td>Take a boat to Aswan's unique ethnic minority village-Nubian Village. Here you can experience the ancient Nubian civilization, visit the colorful houses unique to the Nubians, learn the local language, and visit the home. Includes pick-up and drop-off service from the pier, accompanied by a Chinese-speaking guide, as well as Nubian village specialty drinks and camel riding.<br>50 USD/person (4-7 people)<br>45 USD/person (8 people and above)<br></td></tr><tr><td>Four-wheel Drive Jeep Rushing</td><td>90 USD/person (4-7 people)</td><td>Around 2:30 in the afternoon, take a four-wheel drive from the hotel and head to the desert next door to the eastern part of Egypt for sand washing. Free yourself in the empty next door. Climb to the top of the dunes to enjoy the sunset. Afterwards, head to the ancient Bedouin village to explore the life of the Bedouin. And experience the fun of riding a camel. If you are lucky on the way back, you can see the sky full of stars.<br>Note: This item is an irritating item. The driving process of 4WD vehicles is quite bumpy and there is a certain risk. Please take part carefully! Please pay attention to safety when getting on and off the camel! If the car seat is not equipped with a seat belt, please refuse to board the car and request a refund of the corresponding fee!<br>90 USD/person (4-7 people)<br>80 USD/person (more than 8 people)<br>The expenses include: 4*4 jeep fare, tour guide fee, attraction ticket, BBQ dinner</td></tr><tr><td>Giftun Island Tour</td><td>80 USD/person (over 10 people)</td><td>Depart from the hotel at around 8:30 in the morning, head to the pier, board the yacht, and enter the beautiful Red Sea. Chartered boats do not join other tourists to enjoy the scenery of the Red Sea. Feeding seagulls, fishing, snorkeling and various amusement options. Snorkeling equipment and basic fishing equipment are provided on the yacht. Enjoy a simple lunch on the boat at noon. Including pick-up and drop-off service, accompanied by a Chinese-speaking guide.<br>Note:<br>Please pay attention to safety when you disembark from the sea on a yacht. Do not queue up and slide carefully. The captain and lifeguard should not make dangerous actions before making arrangements. As the yacht is fast and the sea is more bumpy, the elderly, weak, women, children and patients please participate carefully! )<br>80 USD/person (over 10 people)<br></td></tr><tr><td>Sinbad Submarine</td><td>115 USD/person (from 2 people)</td><td>Go to the pier and take a speedboat to the submarine platform. Take a submarine to dive into the 7-meter deep Red Sea and enjoy the mysterious and beautiful underwater world of the Red Sea. And some divers will give you a performance of feeding fish under the sea. Including pick-up and drop-off, accompanied by a Chinese guide<br>Note:<br>This program is an irritating. Due to certain pressure under the sea, for the elderly, weak, women, children and patients please participate carefully!<br>115 USD/person (from 2 people)</td></tr><tr><td>Red Sea Glass Boat Tour</td><td>70 USD/person (from 4 people)</td><td>Take a specially customized cruise ship with large sightseeing windows at the bottom of the cruise ship, which is convenient for enjoying the wonderful underwater world. Includes pick-up and drop-off, accompanied by a Chinese-speaking guide<br>Note:<br>Please pay attention to safety when boarding and disembarking the boat. Do not line up in crowds and slide carefully.<br>70 USD/person (from 4 people)</td></tr><tr><td>Luxor Hot Air Balloon</td><td>165 USD/person (2-3 people)</td><td>Depart from the hotel to the pier at around 5:00 in the morning and take a boat to the west bank of the Nile. Hot coffee, tea, and small snacks are prepared on the boat. Ride a hot air balloon to welcome the sunrise and overlook Luxor. Pass through the Habu City, Queen's Temple, Valley of the Kings and other scenic spots, and experience a different Luxor from a high altitude. After landing, a small celebration ceremony will be held and a certificate will be issued to the guests. Then return to the hotel by private car.<br>Special Note:<br>1. The hot air balloon is a high-risk program, please choose carefully according to your own circumstances.<br>2. The itinerary is for reference only and depends on the specific weather conditions of the day. If the hot air balloon cannot be taken due to weather conditions, the original price will be refunded!<br>3. Children under 7 years old cannot participate in this program<br>4. During the hot air balloon, the team leader and tour guide will not be accompanied at all times. Please wait patiently in order when getting on and off the hot air balloon. Do not rush to get on and off the hot air balloon and make dangerous moves to avoid accidents. Fly and cherish! 165 USD/person (2-3 people)<br><br>150 USD/person (4 people and above)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\">The programs listed above are all suggested programs. The guests choose to participate in the principle of voluntary and self-finance. Some programs may not be able to take part when the number of participants or resources is insufficient.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></dd></dl></div>", 5999.8m, "Zamami Whale Watching One Day Tour in Okinawa, Japan【No Whale No Charge | Naha | Motobu Town | Chatan American Village Whale Watching】", null },
